PART 2ï¸âƒ£ â€” REFINING TABLE UI (BLADE)

1ï¸âƒ£ Basic Table (Before)
<table>
@foreach($users as $user)
<tr>
<td>{{ $user->name }}</td>
<td>{{ $user->email }}</td>
</tr>
@endforeach
</table>

2ï¸âƒ£ Clean Table with Bootstrap / Tailwind
<table class="table table-bordered table-striped">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>#</th>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Email</th>
            <th>Created</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>

    <tbody>
        @foreach($users as $user)
        <tr>
            <td>{{ $loop->iteration }}</td>
            <td>{{ $user->name }}</td>
            <td>{{ $user->email }}</td>
            <td>{{ $user->created_at->format('d M Y') }}</td>
        </tr>
        @endforeach
    </tbody>
</table>

3ï¸âƒ£ Handling Empty Data (IMPORTANT ğŸ”¥)
@forelse($users as $user)
<tr>
    <td>{{ $user->name }}</td>
</tr>
@empty
<tr>
    <td colspan="4" class="text-center">No records found</td>
</tr>
@endforelse

4ï¸âƒ£ Pagination-Friendly Tables

ğŸ“„ Controller

